name: Lifetime
description: typically in use phase, or residence time in landfill etc.

name: Material composition
description: m.c. of products, alloys, waste/scrap, etc.

name: Yield coefficient
description: material or energy yield of processes

name: Intensity of use of products
description: service (physical or immaterial) extracted from products

name: Specific energy consumption of products
description: energy per unit of use of products, e.g., MJ/km of vehicle driven

name: Per capita stock
description: stock per person, e.g., cars per capita

name: Per capita flows
description: flows per persion, e.g., GDP per capita

name: Material substitution coefficient
description: Amount of material 1 substituted by amount of material 2.

name: Process inventory
description: flows entering and leaving process, for LCI datasets

name: Unit process inventory
description: flows entering and leaving process, normalized, for LCI datasets
